'''Liling Agessy''' (née '''Zedong'''; born July 10, 1967) is a Canadian and American marriage counselor and former professional volleyball player. She played for the Vancouver Vans from 1985 to 1999, the Boulder Brownies from 1999 to 2004, and the Detroit Material Girls from 2004 to 2008. 

